{"id":278547,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-小年夜钱琴母女无家可归，倪文华等冒雪/","date":"2013-02-09T00:45:45Z","modified":"2013-02-09T00:45:45Z","title":"维权网 | 小年夜钱琴母女无家可归，倪文华等冒雪赴如皋看望（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）小年夜（<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>）一早，山东济南倪文华与江苏无锡沈爱斌、丁红芬、王建芬以及安徽芜湖周琛等冒雪前往如皋市看望因暴力拆迁而无家可归的钱琴母子。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，在没有任何合法手续的情况下，如皋市如城镇人民政府派城管将钱琴家强拆。当时，钱琴生孩子刚满月，就遭遇了暴力拆迁，现场一片狼藉，孩子受惊吓而住院治疗。</span>  </p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁红芬、王建芬和周琛等在强拆现场的废墟上，联想自己在拆迁中的不幸遭遇，控诉暴力拆迁给钱琴母子和其他拆迁户的巨大伤害。</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>倪文华怒斥如皋市如城镇政府强拆民房的暴行，可谓丧尽天良。当地政府给钱琴一家造成的伤害和痛苦，难以言喻。更令人不可思议的是，如此明火执仗地强拆民房，当地政府竟然矢口否认其强拆行为，政府的公信力何在？</span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8CU138S0hxw/URWSIGqjvyI/AAAAAAAAcdM/zFSCa-3gOFI/s1600/%E9%92%B1%E7%90%B4%E5%BA%9F%E5%A2%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-8CU138S0hxw/URWSIGqjvyI/AAAAAAAAcdM/zFSCa-3gOFI/s400/%E9%92%B1%E7%90%B4%E5%BA%9F%E5%A2%9F%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%B6.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-I0D4GwENnQQ/URWSIJsVPXI/AAAAAAAAcdI/4sVT1dOFWv4/s1600/DSCN1932.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-I0D4GwENnQQ/URWSIJsVPXI/AAAAAAAAcdI/4sVT1dOFWv4/s400/DSCN1932.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-b0bzktBXPEk/URWSIeZ7nAI/AAAAAAAAcdQ/b6SNt8WIPsE/s1600/DSCN1929.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-b0bzktBXPEk/URWSIeZ7nAI/AAAAAAAAcdQ/b6SNt8WIPsE/s400/DSCN1929.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}